CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 16, 1953, pg. 11 reads: "Club 21 - This lovely group of debbies are members of Club 21, the older members of the Jack and Jill. They'll sing and dance in Prologue and Epilogue scenes of the forthcoming Jabberwock, to be given May 22 at the Irene Kaufmann Auditorium by Delta Sigma Theta Sorority.  Pictured are Jeannine Henry, Lois Glass, Louise Hampton, Patricia Knott, Charlotte Carter, Betty Ann Voyson, Barbarann Boswell and, seated, Lyda Jo Boswell. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Eight Delta Sigma Theta Club 21 members, from left, standing: Jeannine Henry, Lois Glass, Louise Hampton, Patricia Knott, Charlotte Carter, Betty Ann Voyson, and Barbarann Boswell; seated: Lyda Jo Boswell; posed of steps of brick church with arched stained glass window, another version
